      "text": "brand partnerships, sponsored posts, affiliate marketing, and digital products"
    },
    {
      "id": "t4",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Depending on follower count and engagement, influencers can earn anywhere from"
    },
    {
      "id": "t5",
