      "text": "Main Ways Instagram Influencers Make Money"
    },
    {
      "id": "t19",
      "tag": "h3",
      "text": "1. Sponsored Posts"
    },
    {
      "id": "t20",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "The most common revenue source for influencers is sponsored content. Brands pay creators to promote products through posts, stories, or reels."
    },
    {
      "id": "t21",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Micro influencers (10K – 50K followers): $100 – $1,500 per post"
    },
    {
      "id": "t22",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Mid-tier influencers (50K – 500K): $1,500 – $10,000"
    },
    {
      "id": "t23",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Large influencers (500K – 1M+): $10,000 – $100,000+"
    },
    {
      "id": "t24",
      "tag": "h3",
      "text": "2. Brand Partnerships"
    },
    {
      "id": "t25",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Some influencers sign long-term partnerships with companies. These deals provide consistent monthly income."
    },
    {
      "id": "t26",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Small creators: $1K – $5K per month"
    },
    {
      "id": "t27",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Mid-tier creators: $5K – $20K per month"
    },
    {
      "id": "t28",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Large creators: $20K – $100K+ per month"
    },
    {
      "id": "t29",
      "tag": "h3",
      "text": "3. Affiliate Marketing"
    },
    {
      "id": "t30",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Many influencers promote products using affiliate links. When followers purchase through these links, the influencer earns a commission."
    },
    {
      "id": "t31",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Affiliate commissions usually range between"
    },
    {
      "id": "t32",
      "tag": "strong",
      "text": "5% and 25%"
    },
    {
      "id": "t33",
      "tag": "h3",
      "text": "4. Selling Digital Products"
    },
    {
      "id": "t34",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Influencers often sell their own digital products such as courses, templates, presets, or memberships."
    },
    {
      "id": "t35",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "This strategy can generate significant recurring revenue once a creator builds a loyal audience."
